text: Nataliya Kolchina also written as Natalja Koltsjina (Russian: Наталья Колчина, born September 1939) is a former Soviet long track speed skater, who was active in the 1960s. Kolchina represented her nation at the World Allround Speed Skating Championships for Women in 1963, finishing 5th overall. She also competed at other international competitions. Between 1962 and 1966 she competed three times at the Soviet Allround Championships. == Records== === Personal records === ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Soviet female speed skaters Category:Living people
